Leccion 5- Where, what (Wh Questions) 

Hello ! My name is Alonso. Today I am in my house, I am resting, My Brother Doris is in the garden planting Flowers. My Sibling, Alejandra, David and Andres are Watching a movie on the bed. 

1- Where = Donde.
2- What = Que, cual, cuales.

Examples:
1- Where is Alonso.
2-Where are siblings.
3-Alonso is in the house.
He is in the house.
4-Where is Alonso resting.
Oracion Afirmativa.
5-Alonso is resting
Oracion negativa. 

6- Is Alonso resting.
7- Doris is planting.
8- What is doris planting.
9- Doris is planting flowers. 

Practicing:


1-Donde esta Alonso?
Where is Alonso.
He is in the house./ Alonso is in the house. 

2- Que esta haciendo Alonso en el sofa. 

What is Alonso doing on the sofa? 

Alonso is resting on the sofa./ He is resting on the sofa. 

3-Que esta plantando Doris. 

What is Doris planting.
Doris is planting Flowers / She is planting Flowers in the garden. 

4-Donde estan sus hermanos. 

Where is his Siblings. 

His siblings are on the bad. 

5- Que estan viendo sus hermanos. 

What are his sibling  Watching  
His sibling are watching a movie/ They are watching a movie. 

6- Esta Alonso en su casa hoy? 

Is Alonso in his house today. 

Yes, he is in his house.